@startuml
title Sprint 2 - Projets et integrations (CRUD, OAuth GitHub, API keys)
actor "Utilisateur" as U
boundary "IHM Projets" as UI
control "ProjectController" as PC
control "ProjectService" as PS
entity "ProjectModel" as PM
database "Base de donnees" as DB

control "IntegrationsController" as IC
control "GitHubOAuthService" as GHO
entity "GitHubRepositoryModel" as GR
control "EncryptionService" as ENC
participant "GitHub OAuth" as GIT
participant "GitHub API" as GHAPI

control "APIKeyController" as AKC
entity "APIKeyModel" as AKM
control "AuditLogService" as ALS

U -> UI: creer projet
UI -> PC: POST /projects
PC -> PS: create_project(dto, owner)
PS -> PM: new Project(...)
PM -> DB: INSERT project
DB --> PM: id
PS --> PC: project
PC --> UI: project details
UI --> U: confirmation

== GitHub OAuth ==
U -> UI: connecter GitHub
UI -> IC: GET /integrations/github/oauth/start
IC -> GHO: generate_oauth_state()
GHO --> IC: state + authorize_url
IC --> UI: authorize_url
UI -> GIT: redirect + consent
GIT --> UI: code + state
UI -> IC: POST /integrations/github/oauth/exchange
IC -> GHO: validate_state + exchange token
GHO -> GHAPI: POST /login/oauth/access_token
GHAPI --> GHO: access_token
GHO --> IC: token
IC -> ENC: encrypt_token(token)
ENC --> IC: encrypted
IC -> GR: upsert repo (project_id, url, branch, token)
GR -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE github_repository
DB --> GR: ok
IC --> UI: connected

opt creer API key CLI
    U -> UI: creer cle API
    UI -> AKC: POST /auth/api-keys
    AKC -> AKM: new API key (hash + prefix)
    AKM -> DB: INSERT api_key
    DB --> AKM: ok
    AKC -> ALS: create_audit_log("api_key_created")
    ALS -> DB: INSERT audit_log
    AKC --> UI: plaintext key (once)
end
@enduml
